body:
@eriophora you can use a placeholder, no need to add code

```
 cti=tf.placeholder(tf.string,shape=(1,1))   
 z=tf.constant(10)                               
 y=tf.Print(z,[cti,z])                    
 with tf.Session() as sess:                                
         for i in range(10):
         time.sleep(1)                          
         ti=time.asctime()    
         xx=np.array([ti],ndmin=2)         
         y.eval(feed_dict={cti:xx}) 
```
